<p>Hi {{GuestDisplayName}},</p>
<p>We've received your reservation request <strong>{{Reference}}</strong> for <strong>{{PropertyTitle}}</strong>. Your card has been authorized but <em>not charged</em> — we wait for the host's confirmation first.</p>

<table style="margin: 12px 0; width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;">Check-in</td><td style="padding: 4px 0; text-align: right;"><strong>{{Checkin}}</strong></td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;">Check-out</td><td style="padding: 4px 0; text-align: right;"><strong>{{Checkout}}</strong></td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;">Nights</td><td style="padding: 4px 0; text-align: right;"><strong>{{Nights}}</strong></td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;">Guests</td><td style="padding: 4px 0; text-align: right;"><strong>{{GuestCount}}</strong></td></tr>
</table>

<table style="margin: 12px 0; width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
  <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;">Subtotal</td><td style="padding: 4px 0; text-align: right;">{{Currency}} {{Subtotal}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;">Fees</td><td style="padding: 4px 0; text-align: right;">{{Currency}} {{Fees}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding: 4px 0;">Taxes</td><td style="padding: 4px 0; text-align: right;">{{Currency}} {{Taxes}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding: 8px 0 4px;"><strong>Total authorized</strong></td><td style="padding: 8px 0 4px; text-align: right;"><strong>{{Currency}} {{Total}}</strong></td></tr>
</table>

<p>Decision deadline: <strong>{{TentativeUntil}}</strong>. Cancellation policy: <strong>{{CancellationPolicy}}</strong>.</p>
<p>If the host doesn't respond by the deadline, the booking is auto-confirmed unless there's a calendar conflict (in which case it's cancelled, your hold released, no charge).</p>
<p>You'll get another email when the host responds.</p>
